Oh amongst themselves I think and - and their - and their - senior members of the - of the churches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11538388 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid816629\charrsid11435002 What about the teachers in those days, who would they associate with?
